        'pf3fgssqsqkujzhwwvld' => [
            'title' => 'La petite annonce du Professeur Saibou',
            'numero' => 3,
            'description' => '<div><span class="highlight author-d-iz88z86z86za0dz67zz78zz78zz74zz68zjz80zz71z9iz90z9pej8mjj94z76z67rz68zkpz82z1z68z0z73zz83zdz81zz84zxaz71zpd" data-highlight-color="#D6E8FA">La petite annonce du Professeur Saibou, un expert multi-domaines au champ de comp&eacute;tences presque infini.</span> <span class="highlight author-d-iz88z86z86za0dz67zz78zz78zz74zz68zjz80zz71z9iz90z9pej8mjj94z76z67rz68zkpz82z1z68z0z73zz83zdz81zz84zxaz71zpd h-ldquo" data-highlight-color="#D6E8FA">&ldquo;Sp&eacute;cialiste</span><span class="highlight author-d-iz88z86z86za0dz67zz78zz78zz74zz68zjz80zz71z9iz90z9pej8mjj94z76z67rz68zkpz82z1z68z0z73zz83zdz81zz84zxaz71zpd" data-highlight-color="#D6E8FA"> de tout&rdquo;</span> <span class="highlight author-d-iz88z86z86za0dz67zz78zz78zz74zz68zjz80zz71z9iz90z9pej8mjj94z76z67rz68zkpz82z1z68z0z73zz83zdz81zz84zxaz71zpd h-lparen" data-highlight-color="#D6E8FA">(sic),</span><span class="highlight author-d-iz88z86z86za0dz67zz78zz78zz74zz68zjz80zz71z9iz90z9pej8mjj94z76z67rz68zkpz82z1z68z0z73zz83zdz81zz84zxaz71zpd" data-highlight-color="#D6E8FA"> le professeur a non seulement un liste de comp&eacute;tences &agrave; faire rougir le plus costaud des CV, mais il est &eacute;galement</span> <span class="highlight author-d-iz88z86z86za0dz67zz78zz78zz74zz68zjz80zz71z9iz90z9pej8mjj94z76z67rz68zkpz82z1z68z0z73zz83zdz81zz84zxaz71zpd h-ldquo" data-highlight-color="#D6E8FA">&ldquo;s&eacute;rieux,</span><span class="highlight author-d-iz88z86z86za0dz67zz78zz78zz74zz68zjz80zz71z9iz90z9pej8mjj94z76z67rz68zkpz82z1z68z0z73zz83zdz81zz84zxaz71zpd" data-highlight-color="#D6E8FA"> rapide, honn&ecirc;te et discret&rdquo;</span> <span class="highlight author-d-iz88z86z86za0dz67zz78zz78zz74zz68zjz80zz71z9iz90z9pej8mjj94z76z67rz68zkpz82z1z68z0z73zz83zdz81zz84zxaz71zpd h-lparen" data-highlight-color="#D6E8FA">(les</span><span class="highlight author-d-iz88z86z86za0dz67zz78zz78zz74zz68zjz80zz71z9iz90z9pej8mjj94z76z67rz68zkpz82z1z68z0z73zz83zdz81zz84zxaz71zpd" data-highlight-color="#D6E8FA"> fameux</span> <span class="highlight author-d-iz88z86z86za0dz67zz78zz78zz74zz68zjz80zz71z9iz90z9pbz87zqoe2z88zcte9z66zuwp2qz69z0oa7rz79zz77zsl0z80z h-ldquo" data-highlight-color="#D6E8FA">&ldquo;</span><span class="highlight author-d-iz88z86z86za0dz67zz78zz78zz74zz68zjz80zz71z9iz90z9pej8mjj94z76z67rz68zkpz82z1z68z0z73zz83zdz81zz84zxaz71zpd h-ldquo" data-highlight-color="#D6E8FA">soft-skills</span><span class="highlight author-d-iz88z86z86za0dz67zz78zz78zz74zz68zjz80zz71z9iz90z9pbz87zqoe2z88zcte9z66zuwp2qz69z0oa7rz79zz77zsl0z80z h-ldquo" data-highlight-color="#D6E8FA">&rdquo;</span><span class="highlight author-d-iz88z86z86za0dz67zz78zz78zz74zz68zjz80zz71z9iz90z9pej8mjj94z76z67rz68zkpz82z1z68z0z73zz83zdz81zz84zxaz71zpd" data-highlight-color="#D6E8FA"> ou</span> <span class="highlight author-d-iz88z86z86za0dz67zz78zz78zz74zz68zjz80zz71z9iz90z9pbz87zqoe2z88zcte9z66zuwp2qz69z0oa7rz79zz77zsl0z80z h-ldquo" data-highlight-color="#D6E8FA">&ldquo;</span><span class="highlight author-d-iz88z86z86za0dz67zz78zz78zz74zz68zjz80zz71z9iz90z9pej8mjj94z76z67rz68zkpz82z1z68z0z73zz83zdz81zz84zxaz71zpd h-ldquo" data-highlight-color="#D6E8FA">savoir-&ecirc;tre</span><span class="highlight author-d-iz88z86z86za0dz67zz78zz78zz74zz68zjz80zz71z9iz90z9pbz87zqoe2z88zcte9z66zuwp2qz69z0oa7rz79zz77zsl0z80z h-ldquo" data-highlight-color="#D6E8FA">&rdquo;</span><span class="highlight author-d-iz88z86z86za0dz67zz78zz78zz74zz68zjz80zz71z9iz90z9pej8mjj94z76z67rz68zkpz82z1z68z0z73zz83zdz81zz84zxaz71zpd" data-highlight-color="#D6E8FA"> qui comptent tellement aujourd&rsquo;hui). Un candidat id&eacute;al, que tout recruteur souhaite avoir en entretien&hellip;</span></div>',
            'why' => '<p><span class="highlight author-d-iz88z86z86za0dz67zz78zz78zz74zz68zjz80zz71z9iz90z9pej8mjj94z76z67rz68zkpz82z1z68z0z73zz83zdz81zz84zxaz71zpd" data-highlight-color="#D6E8FA">Parce que </span><span class="highlight author-d-iz88z86z86za0dz67zz78zz78zz74zz68zjz80zz71z9iz90z9pbz87zqoe2z88zcte9z66zuwp2qz69z0oa7rz79zz77zsl0z80z" data-highlight-color="#D6E8FA">c</span><span class="highlight author-d-iz88z86z86za0dz67zz78zz78zz74zz68zjz80zz71z9iz90z9pej8mjj94z76z67rz68zkpz82z1z68z0z73zz83zdz81zz84zxaz71zpd" data-highlight-color="#D6E8FA">ette petite annonce pose</span><span class="highlight author-d-iz88z86z86za0dz67zz78zz78zz74zz68zjz80zz71z9iz90z9pbz87zqoe2z88zcte9z66zuwp2qz69z0oa7rz79zz77zsl0z80z" data-highlight-color="#D6E8FA"> finalement</span><span class="highlight author-d-iz88z86z86za0dz67zz78zz78zz74zz68zjz80zz71z9iz90z9pej8mjj94z76z67rz68zkpz82z1z68z0z73zz83zdz81zz84zxaz71zpd" data-highlight-color="#D6E8FA"> la question des comp&eacute;tences et de l&rsquo;employabilit&eacute;. Dans son rapport sur l&rsquo;emploi des jeunes de 2013, l&rsquo;OIT soulignait</span> <span class="highlight author-d-iz88z86z86za0dz67zz78zz78zz74zz68zjz80zz71z9iz90z9pej8mjj94z76z67rz68zkpz82z1z68z0z73zz83zdz81zz84zxaz71zpd h-ldquo" data-highlight-color="#D6E8FA">&ldquo;l&rsquo;inad&eacute;quation</span><span class="highlight author-d-iz88z86z86za0dz67zz78zz78zz74zz68zjz80zz71z9iz90z9pej8mjj94z76z67rz68zkpz82z1z68z0z73zz83zdz81zz84zxaz71zpd" data-highlight-color="#D6E8FA"> &nbsp;des &nbsp;comp&eacute;tences &nbsp;entre &nbsp;l\'offre &nbsp;et &nbsp;la &nbsp;demande &nbsp;de &nbsp;main‐d\'&oelig;uvre &nbsp;sur &nbsp;les &nbsp;march&eacute;s &nbsp;du &nbsp;travail &nbsp;des &nbsp;jeunes. &nbsp;La&nbsp; sur&eacute;ducation &nbsp;et &nbsp;la &nbsp;surqualification &nbsp;coexistent &nbsp;avec &nbsp;la &nbsp;sous‐&eacute;ducation &nbsp;et &nbsp;la &nbsp;sous‐ qualification, &nbsp;et &nbsp;de &nbsp;plus &nbsp;en &nbsp;plus &nbsp;avec &nbsp;l&rsquo;obsolescence &nbsp;des &nbsp;comp&eacute;tences &nbsp;qu&rsquo;entra&icirc;ne &nbsp;le &nbsp;ch&ocirc;mage de longue dur&eacute;e&rdquo;.&nbsp;</span></p>
<p><span class="highlight author-d-iz88z86z86za0dz67zz78zz78zz74zz68zjz80zz71z9iz90z9pej8mjj94z76z67rz68zkpz82z1z68z0z73zz83zdz81zz84zxaz71zpd" data-highlight-color="#D6E8FA">Depuis, une &eacute;tude <span class="highlight author-d-iz88z86z86za0dz67zz78zz78zz74zz68zjz80zz71z9iz90z9pbz87zqoe2z88zcte9z66zuwp2qz69z0oa7rz79zz77zsl0z80z" data-highlight-color="#D6E8FA">d</span>e Deloitte a montr&eacute; que la dur&eacute;e d<span class="highlight author-d-iz88z86z86za0dz67zz78zz78zz74zz68zjz80zz71z9iz90z9pbz87zqoe2z88zcte9z66zuwp2qz69z0oa7rz79zz77zsl0z80z" data-highlight-color="#D6E8FA">&rsquo;une demi-</span>vie d&rsquo;une comp&eacute;tence professionnelle ne d&eacute;passait pas 5 ans. Nous vivons donc actuellement une p&eacute;riode paradoxale dans laquelle l&rsquo;important investissement en temps et en argent que repr&eacute;sentent les &eacute;tudes sup&eacute;rieures n&rsquo;aboutit pas &agrave; des d&eacute;bouch&eacute;s satisfaisants : <span class="highlight author-d-iz88z86z86za0dz67zz78zz78zz74zz68zjz80zz71z9iz90z9pbz87zqoe2z88zcte9z66zuwp2qz69z0oa7rz79zz77zsl0z80z" data-highlight-color="#D6E8FA">certains </span>jeunes finiront <span class="highlight author-d-iz88z86z86za0dz67zz78zz78zz74zz68zjz80zz71z9iz90z9pbz87zqoe2z88zcte9z66zuwp2qz69z0oa7rz79zz77zsl0z80z" data-highlight-color="#D6E8FA">par </span>exercer des emplois qui ne requi&egrave;rent pas les comp&eacute;tences pointues qu&rsquo;ils ont acquises. C&rsquo;est ce que certains ont appel&eacute; <span class="highlight author-d-iz88z86z86za0dz67zz78zz78zz74zz68zjz80zz71z9iz90z9pej8mjj94z76z67rz68zkpz82z1z68z0z73zz83zdz81zz84zxaz71zpd h-ldquo" data-highlight-color="#D6E8FA">&ldquo;l&rsquo;&egrave;re</span> des baristas avec des doctorats&rdquo; <span class="highlight author-d-iz88z86z86za0dz67zz78zz78zz74zz68zjz80zz71z9iz90z9pej8mjj94z76z67rz68zkpz82z1z68z0z73zz83zdz81zz84zxaz71zpd h-lparen" data-highlight-color="#D6E8FA">(Derek</span> Thomson).</span></p>',
            'learnmore' => '<p><span class="highlight author-d-iz88z86z86za0dz67zz78zz78zz74zz68zjz80zz71z9iz90z9pej8mjj94z76z67rz68zkpz82z1z68z0z73zz83zdz81zz84zxaz71zpd" data-highlight-color="#D6E8FA">Alors que les jeunes n&rsquo;ont jamais fait autant d&rsquo;&eacute;tudes, le taux de ch&ocirc;mage des 15-24 ans est actuellement de pr&egrave;s de 25%, et 5 &agrave; 10% d&rsquo;entre eux sont sous-employ&eacute;s en France. En outre, selon l&rsquo;OCDE, plus de 50% des jeunes travailleurs</span> <span class="highlight author-d-iz88z86z86za0dz67zz78zz78zz74zz68zjz80zz71z9iz90z9pej8mjj94z76z67rz68zkpz82z1z68z0z73zz83zdz81zz84zxaz71zpd h-lparen" data-highlight-color="#D6E8FA">(15-24</span><span class="highlight author-d-iz88z86z86za0dz67zz78zz78zz74zz68zjz80zz71z9iz90z9pej8mjj94z76z67rz68zkpz82z1z68z0z73zz83zdz81zz84zxaz71zpd" data-highlight-color="#D6E8FA"> ans) sont condamn&eacute;s &agrave; prendre des emplois de nature temporaire. Dans</span> <span class="highlight author-d-iz88z86z86za0dz67zz78zz78zz74zz68zjz80zz71z9iz90z9pej8mjj94z76z67rz68zkpz82z1z68z0z73zz83zdz81zz84zxaz71zpd h-ldquo" data-highlight-color="#D6E8FA">&ldquo;Le</span><span class="highlight author-d-iz88z86z86za0dz67zz78zz78zz74zz68zjz80zz71z9iz90z9pej8mjj94z76z67rz68zkpz82z1z68z0z73zz83zdz81zz84zxaz71zpd" data-highlight-color="#D6E8FA"> d&eacute;bat sur la retraite en France : le crit&egrave;re interg&eacute;n&eacute;rationnel aide-t-il &agrave; trancher ?&rdquo;, Didier Blancher s&rsquo;inqui&egrave;te d&rsquo;une</span> <span class="highlight author-d-iz88z86z86za0dz67zz78zz78zz74zz68zjz80zz71z9iz90z9pej8mjj94z76z67rz68zkpz82z1z68z0z73zz83zdz81zz84zxaz71zpd h-ldquo" data-highlight-color="#D6E8FA">&ldquo;in&eacute;quit&eacute;</span><span class="highlight author-d-iz88z86z86za0dz67zz78zz78zz74zz68zjz80zz71z9iz90z9pej8mjj94z76z67rz68zkpz82z1z68z0z73zz83zdz81zz84zxaz71zpd" data-highlight-color="#D6E8FA"> g&eacute;n&eacute;rationnelle&rdquo; soit une rupture du contrat social entre deux g&eacute;n&eacute;rations. La formule parait forte, car la question de l&rsquo;acquisition des comp&eacute;tences touche les jeunes comme les moins jeunes. Mais comme le note l&rsquo;OIT,</span> <span class="highlight author-d-iz88z86z86za0dz67zz78zz78zz74zz68zjz80zz71z9iz90z9pej8mjj94z76z67rz68zkpz82z1z68z0z73zz83zdz81zz84zxaz71zpd h-ldquo" data-highlight-color="#D6E8FA">&ldquo;il</span><span class="highlight author-d-iz88z86z86za0dz67zz78zz78zz74zz68zjz80zz71z9iz90z9pej8mjj94z76z67rz68zkpz82z1z68z0z73zz83zdz81zz84zxaz71zpd" data-highlight-color="#D6E8FA"> existe, pour les jeunes particuli&egrave;rement, une tendance pernicieuse vers des emplois pr&eacute;caires et de faible qualit&eacute; qui n&rsquo;offrent ni la s&eacute;curit&eacute; du revenu ni le d&eacute;veloppement professionnel souhait&eacute;. Dans le monde, c&rsquo;est une g&eacute;n&eacute;ration enti&egrave;re qui se retrouve &agrave; faire face au ch&ocirc;mage et au sous-emploi.&rdquo;</span></p>',
