        'gsqsqe3hk42rkq2uc2ki' => [
            'title' => 'Un métier à tisser',
            'numero' => 1,
            'description' => '<p><span class="highlight thread-490377651712028944180413 author-d-iz88z86z86za0dz67zz78zz78zz74zz68zjz80zz71z9iz90z9pej8mjj94z76z67rz68zkpz82z1z68z0z73zz83zdz81zz84zxaz71zpd" data-highlight-color="#D6E8FA">Un m&eacute;tier &agrave; tisser DIY</span> <span class="highlight thread-490377651712028944180413 author-d-iz88z86z86za0dz67zz78zz78zz74zz68zjz80zz71z9iz90z9pej8mjj94z76z67rz68zkpz82z1z68z0z73zz83zdz81zz84zxaz71zpd h-lparen" data-highlight-color="#D6E8FA">(Do</span><span class="highlight thread-490377651712028944180413 author-d-iz88z86z86za0dz67zz78zz78zz74zz68zjz80zz71z9iz90z9pej8mjj94z76z67rz68zkpz82z1z68z0z73zz83zdz81zz84zxaz71zpd" data-highlight-color="#D6E8FA"> It Yourself). &nbsp;En Angleterre,</span><span class="highlight author-d-iz88z86z86za0dz67zz78zz78zz74zz68zjz80zz71z9iz90z9pbz87zqoe2z88zcte9z66zuwp2qz69z0oa7rz79zz77zsl0z80z" data-highlight-color="#D6E8FA">dans les ann&eacute;es 1811-1812</span><span class="highlight author-d-iz88z86z86za0dz67zz78zz78zz74zz68zjz80zz71z9iz90z9pej8mjj94z76z67rz68zkpz82z1z68z0z73zz83zdz81zz84zxaz71zpd" data-highlight-color="#D6E8FA">, les m&eacute;tiers &agrave; tisser ont &eacute;t&eacute; le symbole d&rsquo;</span><span class="highlight author-d-iz88z86z86za0dz67zz78zz78zz74zz68zjz80zz71z9iz90z9pbz87zqoe2z88zcte9z66zuwp2qz69z0oa7rz79zz77zsl0z80z" data-highlight-color="#D6E8FA">un conflit industriel violent</span><span class="highlight author-d-iz88z86z86za0dz67zz78zz78zz74zz68zjz80zz71z9iz90z9pej8mjj94z76z67rz68zkpz82z1z68z0z73zz83zdz81zz84zxaz71zpd" data-highlight-color="#D6E8FA"> entre</span> <span class="highlight author-d-iz88z86z86za0dz67zz78zz78zz74zz68zjz80zz71z9iz90z9pej8mjj94z76z67rz68zkpz82z1z68z0z73zz83zdz81zz84zxaz71zpd" data-highlight-color="#D6E8FA">les</span><span class="highlight author-d-iz88z86z86za0dz67zz78zz78zz74zz68zjz80zz71z9iz90z9pbz87zqoe2z88zcte9z66zuwp2qz69z0oa7rz79zz77zsl0z80z" data-highlight-color="#D6E8FA"> artisans </span><span class="highlight author-d-iz88z86z86za0dz67zz78zz78zz74zz68zjz80zz71z9iz90z9pej8mjj94z76z67rz68zkpz82z1z68z0z73zz83zdz81zz84zxaz71zpd" data-highlight-color="#D6E8FA">et les</span><span class="highlight author-d-iz88z86z86za0dz67zz78zz78zz74zz68zjz80zz71z9iz90z9pbz87zqoe2z88zcte9z66zuwp2qz69z0oa7rz79zz77zsl0z80z" data-highlight-color="#D6E8FA"> employeurs qui favorisaient l\'emploi de machines dans le travail de la laine et du coton.</span><span class="highlight author-d-iz88z86z86za0dz67zz78zz78zz74zz68zjz80zz71z9iz90z9pej8mjj94z76z67rz68zkpz82z1z68z0z73zz83zdz81zz84zxaz71zpd" data-highlight-color="#D6E8FA"> Ce conflit a donn&eacute; naissance au mouvement du Luddisme. </span><span class="highlight author-d-iz88z86z86za0dz67zz78zz78zz74zz68zjz80zz71z9iz90z9pbz87zqoe2z88zcte9z66zuwp2qz69z0oa7rz79zz77zsl0z80z" data-highlight-color="#D6E8FA">Le terme trouve son origine dans le nom d\'un ouvrier anglais, Ned Ludd qui aurait d&eacute;truit deux m&eacute;tiers &agrave; tisser en 1780</span><span class="highlight author-d-iz88z86z86za0dz67zz78zz78zz74zz68zjz80zz71z9iz90z9pej8mjj94z76z67rz68zkpz82z1z68z0z73zz83zdz81zz84zxaz71zpd" data-highlight-color="#D6E8FA">. &nbsp;Depuis, l</span><span class="highlight author-d-iz88z86z86za0dz67zz78zz78zz74zz68zjz80zz71z9iz90z9pbz87zqoe2z88zcte9z66zuwp2qz69z0oa7rz79zz77zsl0z80z" data-highlight-color="#D6E8FA">e terme</span><span class="highlight author-d-iz88z86z86za0dz67zz78zz78zz74zz68zjz80zz71z9iz90z9pej8mjj94z76z67rz68zkpz82z1z68z0z73zz83zdz81zz84zxaz71zpd" data-highlight-color="#D6E8FA"> de&rdquo;</span><span class="highlight author-d-iz88z86z86za0dz67zz78zz78zz74zz68zjz80zz71z9iz90z9pbz87zqoe2z88zcte9z66zuwp2qz69z0oa7rz79zz77zsl0z80z" data-highlight-color="#D6E8FA">luddism</span><span class="highlight author-d-iz88z86z86za0dz67zz78zz78zz74zz68zjz80zz71z9iz90z9pej8mjj94z76z67rz68zkpz82z1z68z0z73zz83zdz81zz84zxaz71zpd" data-highlight-color="#D6E8FA">e&rdquo;</span><span class="highlight author-d-iz88z86z86za0dz67zz78zz78zz74zz68zjz80zz71z9iz90z9pbz87zqoe2z88zcte9z66zuwp2qz69z0oa7rz79zz77zsl0z80z" data-highlight-color="#D6E8FA"> est parfois utilis&eacute; pour d&eacute;signer ceux qui s\'opposent aux nouvelles technologies ou critiquent celles-ci.</span> <span class="highlight author-d-iz88z86z86za0dz67zz78zz78zz74zz68zjz80zz71z9iz90z9pbz87zqoe2z88zcte9z66zuwp2qz69z0oa7rz79zz77zsl0z80z" data-highlight-color="#D6E8FA">&nbsp;En m&ecirc;me temps, cet objet en mode DIY</span> <span class="highlight author-d-iz88z86z86za0dz67zz78zz78zz74zz68zjz80zz71z9iz90z9pbz87zqoe2z88zcte9z66zuwp2qz69z0oa7rz79zz77zsl0z80z h-lparen" data-highlight-color="#D6E8FA">(&laquo;</span> <span class="highlight thread-295117657585293243926336 author-d-iz88z86z86za0dz67zz78zz78zz74zz68zjz80zz71z9iz90z9pbz87zqoe2z88zcte9z66zuwp2qz69z0oa7rz79zz77zsl0z80z" data-highlight-color="#D6E8FA">Do It Yourself</span><span class="highlight author-d-iz88z86z86za0dz67zz78zz78zz74zz68zjz80zz71z9iz90z9pbz87zqoe2z88zcte9z66zuwp2qz69z0oa7rz79zz77zsl0z80z" data-highlight-color="#D6E8FA"> &raquo;) &eacute;voque les nouveaux mouvements et &laquo; philosophies &raquo; qui visent &agrave; trouver des solutions pour faire le maximum de choses par soi-m&ecirc;me, retrouver un savoir-faire abandonn&eacute; et &eacute;changer des connaissances.</span></p>',
            'why' => '<p><span class="highlight author-d-iz88z86z86za0dz67zz78zz78zz74zz68zjz80zz71z9iz90z9pej8mjj94z76z67rz68zkpz82z1z68z0z73zz83zdz81zz84zxaz71zpd" data-highlight-color="#D6E8FA">Parce que faire l&rsquo;histoire peut apporter un &eacute;clairage sur les mutations que nous vivons actuellement. Le luddisme a &eacute;t&eacute; pendant des d&eacute;cennies le symbole du remplacement de certaines t&acirc;ches par des machines. Et demain ? </span><span class="highlight author-d-iz88z86z86za0dz67zz78zz78zz74zz68zjz80zz71z9iz90z9pbz87zqoe2z88zcte9z66zuwp2qz69z0oa7rz79zz77zsl0z80z" data-highlight-color="#D6E8FA">A quoi ressembleront nos emplois ? Convaincus que le progr&egrave;s technologique apportera le meilleur, les techno-optimistes d&eacute;crivent un monde o&ugrave; les robots occuperont les t&acirc;ches les plus ingrates tandis que les humains se consacreront &agrave; leurs loisirs. Les techno-pessimistes, </span><span class="highlight author-d-iz88z86z86za0dz67zz78zz78zz74zz68zjz80zz71z9iz90z9pej8mjj94z76z67rz68zkpz82z1z68z0z73zz83zdz81zz84zxaz71zpd" data-highlight-color="#D6E8FA">ou n&eacute;o-luddistes, </span><span class="highlight author-d-iz88z86z86za0dz67zz78zz78zz74zz68zjz80zz71z9iz90z9pbz87zqoe2z88zcte9z66zuwp2qz69z0oa7rz79zz77zsl0z80z" data-highlight-color="#D6E8FA">eux, penchent pour un sc&eacute;nario o&ugrave; l&rsquo;intelligence artificielle</span> <span class="highlight author-d-iz88z86z86za0dz67zz78zz78zz74zz68zjz80zz71z9iz90z9pbz87zqoe2z88zcte9z66zuwp2qz69z0oa7rz79zz77zsl0z80z h-lparen" data-highlight-color="#D6E8FA">(IA)</span><span class="highlight author-d-iz88z86z86za0dz67zz78zz78zz74zz68zjz80zz71z9iz90z9pbz87zqoe2z88zcte9z66zuwp2qz69z0oa7rz79zz77zsl0z80z" data-highlight-color="#D6E8FA"> d&eacute;truira massivement les emplois, engendrant pauvret&eacute;, conflits de classes et instabilit&eacute; politique. Dans</span> <span class="highlight author-d-iz88z86z86za0dz67zz78zz78zz74zz68zjz80zz71z9iz90z9pej8mjj94z76z67rz68zkpz82z1z68z0z73zz83zdz81zz84zxaz71zpd h-ldquo" data-highlight-color="#D6E8FA">&ldquo;</span><span class="highlight author-d-iz88z86z86za0dz67zz78zz78zz74zz68zjz80zz71z9iz90z9pbz87zqoe2z88zcte9z66zuwp2qz69z0oa7rz79zz77zsl0z80z h-ldquo" data-highlight-color="#D6E8FA">L&rsquo;Avenir</span><span class="highlight author-d-iz88z86z86za0dz67zz78zz78zz74zz68zjz80zz71z9iz90z9pbz87zqoe2z88zcte9z66zuwp2qz69z0oa7rz79zz77zsl0z80z" data-highlight-color="#D6E8FA"> du travail</span><span class="highlight author-d-iz88z86z86za0dz67zz78zz78zz74zz68zjz80zz71z9iz90z9pej8mjj94z76z67rz68zkpz82z1z68z0z73zz83zdz81zz84zxaz71zpd" data-highlight-color="#D6E8FA">&rdquo;</span><span class="highlight author-d-iz88z86z86za0dz67zz78zz78zz74zz68zjz80zz71z9iz90z9pbz87zqoe2z88zcte9z66zuwp2qz69z0oa7rz79zz77zsl0z80z" data-highlight-color="#D6E8FA">, rapport publi&eacute; en avril 2019, l&rsquo;Organisation de coop&eacute;ration et de d&eacute;veloppement &eacute;conomiques</span> <span class="highlight author-d-iz88z86z86za0dz67zz78zz78zz74zz68zjz80zz71z9iz90z9pbz87zqoe2z88zcte9z66zuwp2qz69z0oa7rz79zz77zsl0z80z h-lparen" data-highlight-color="#D6E8FA">(OCDE)</span><span class="highlight author-d-iz88z86z86za0dz67zz78zz78zz74zz68zjz80zz71z9iz90z9pbz87zqoe2z88zcte9z66zuwp2qz69z0oa7rz79zz77zsl0z80z" data-highlight-color="#D6E8FA"> estime que l\'automatisation menacera 14% des emplois actuels au cours des 15 &agrave; 20 prochaines ann&eacute;es et que 32% des emplois actuels sont susceptibles d\'&ecirc;tre</span> <span class="highlight author-d-iz88z86z86za0dz67zz78zz78zz74zz68zjz80zz71z9iz90z9pbz87zqoe2z88zcte9z66zuwp2qz69z0oa7rz79zz77zsl0z80z h-laquo" data-highlight-color="#D6E8FA">&laquo;profond&eacute;ment</span><span class="highlight author-d-iz88z86z86za0dz67zz78zz78zz74zz68zjz80zz71z9iz90z9pbz87zqoe2z88zcte9z66zuwp2qz69z0oa7rz79zz77zsl0z80z" data-highlight-color="#D6E8FA"> transform&eacute;s&raquo;.&nbsp;</span></p>',
            'learnmore' => '<p><span class="highlight author-d-iz88z86z86za0dz67zz78zz78zz74zz68zjz80zz71z9iz90z9pej8mjj94z76z67rz68zkpz82z1z68z0z73zz83zdz81zz84zxaz71zpd" data-highlight-color="#D6E8FA">D</span><span class="highlight author-d-iz88z86z86za0dz67zz78zz78zz74zz68zjz80zz71z9iz90z9pbz87zqoe2z88zcte9z66zuwp2qz69z0oa7rz79zz77zsl0z80z" data-highlight-color="#D6E8FA">ans les ann&eacute;es 1811-1812</span><span class="highlight author-d-iz88z86z86za0dz67zz78zz78zz74zz68zjz80zz71z9iz90z9pej8mjj94z76z67rz68zkpz82z1z68z0z73zz83zdz81zz84zxaz71zpd" data-highlight-color="#D6E8FA"> en Angleterre, le m&eacute;tier &agrave; tisser a &eacute;t&eacute; le symbole de la lutte entre le</span><span class="highlight author-d-iz88z86z86za0dz67zz78zz78zz74zz68zjz80zz71z9iz90z9pbz87zqoe2z88zcte9z66zuwp2qz69z0oa7rz79zz77zsl0z80z" data-highlight-color="#D6E8FA">s artisans </span><span class="highlight author-d-iz88z86z86za0dz67zz78zz78zz74zz68zjz80zz71z9iz90z9pej8mjj94z76z67rz68zkpz82z1z68z0z73zz83zdz81zz84zxaz71zpd" data-highlight-color="#D6E8FA">manuels </span><span class="highlight author-d-iz88z86z86za0dz67zz78zz78zz74zz68zjz80zz71z9iz90z9pbz87zqoe2z88zcte9z66zuwp2qz69z0oa7rz79zz77zsl0z80z" data-highlight-color="#D6E8FA">&mdash; tondeurs et tricoteurs sur m&eacute;tiers &agrave; bras du West Riding, du Lancashire du sud et d\'une partie du Leicestershire et du Derbyshire &mdash; </span><span class="highlight author-d-iz88z86z86za0dz67zz78zz78zz74zz68zjz80zz71z9iz90z9pej8mjj94z76z67rz68zkpz82z1z68z0z73zz83zdz81zz84zxaz71zpd" data-highlight-color="#D6E8FA">et les</span><span class="highlight author-d-iz88z86z86za0dz67zz78zz78zz74zz68zjz80zz71z9iz90z9pbz87zqoe2z88zcte9z66zuwp2qz69z0oa7rz79zz77zsl0z80z" data-highlight-color="#D6E8FA"> employeurs et manufacturiers qui favorisaient l\'emploi de </span><span class="highlight author-d-iz88z86z86za0dz67zz78zz78zz74zz68zjz80zz71z9iz90z9pej8mjj94z76z67rz68zkpz82z1z68z0z73zz83zdz81zz84zxaz71zpd" data-highlight-color="#D6E8FA">m&eacute;tiers m&eacute;caniques</span><span class="highlight author-d-iz88z86z86za0dz67zz78zz78zz74zz68zjz80zz71z9iz90z9pbz87zqoe2z88zcte9z66zuwp2qz69z0oa7rz79zz77zsl0z80z" data-highlight-color="#D6E8FA">). La lutte des membres de ce mouvement clandestin, appel&eacute;s luddites ou luddistes, s\'est caract&eacute;ris&eacute;e par les &laquo; briseurs de machines &raquo;.</span><span class="highlight author-d-iz88z86z86za0dz67zz78zz78zz74zz68zjz80zz71z9iz90z9pej8mjj94z76z67rz68zkpz82z1z68z0z73zz83zdz81zz84zxaz71zpd" data-highlight-color="#D6E8FA"> R&eacute;el ou non, </span><span class="highlight author-d-iz88z86z86za0dz67zz78zz78zz74zz68zjz80zz71z9iz90z9pbz87zqoe2z88zcte9z66zuwp2qz69z0oa7rz79zz77zsl0z80z" data-highlight-color="#D6E8FA">Ned Ludd</span><span class="highlight author-d-iz88z86z86za0dz67zz78zz78zz74zz68zjz80zz71z9iz90z9pej8mjj94z76z67rz68zkpz82z1z68z0z73zz83zdz81zz84zxaz71zpd" data-highlight-color="#D6E8FA">, &agrave; l&rsquo;origine du mouvement,</span><span class="highlight author-d-iz88z86z86za0dz67zz78zz78zz74zz68zjz80zz71z9iz90z9pbz87zqoe2z88zcte9z66zuwp2qz69z0oa7rz79zz77zsl0z80z" data-highlight-color="#D6E8FA"> est devenu </span><span class="highlight author-d-iz88z86z86za0dz67zz78zz78zz74zz68zjz80zz71z9iz90z9pej8mjj94z76z67rz68zkpz82z1z68z0z73zz83zdz81zz84zxaz71zpd" data-highlight-color="#D6E8FA">un</span><span class="highlight author-d-iz88z86z86za0dz67zz78zz78zz74zz68zjz80zz71z9iz90z9pbz87zqoe2z88zcte9z66zuwp2qz69z0oa7rz79zz77zsl0z80z" data-highlight-color="#D6E8FA"> leader imaginaire dans un contexte o&ugrave; un leader d&eacute;clar&eacute; serait tomb&eacute; rapidement, victime de la r&eacute;pression.</span><span class="highlight author-d-iz88z86z86za0dz67zz78zz78zz74zz68zjz80zz71z9iz90z9pej8mjj94z76z67rz68zkpz82z1z68z0z73zz83zdz81zz84zxaz71zpd" data-highlight-color="#D6E8FA">&nbsp;</span></p>',
